{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-20327/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-20327"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["2:03:27"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["low key"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man rests his head in a woman's lap as she cradles his face."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-20327","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-20327"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1/ed1ff5df-e774-45e3-af96-dada4e625a43","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:08:32.772Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds’s position, lying on the couch with his head in Alma’s lap, as she strokes his back, evokes a dog curled up with their owner. It is an act of submission, lying with his eyes closed in her lap, trusting her to care for him. This offers a conclusion to the comparison between Reynolds and a dog—here, we see he has been fully domesticated, left at Alma's mercy.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:552.0394736842104,213.55487440191382,1171.0294557416269,530.7887260765551"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1/f2a79d26-4b4b-44fc-8908-28d862f503c1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:08:53.234Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma holds Reynolds’s head as a mother might hold that of her sick son, underscoring <em>Phantom </em>Thread’s Freudian themes. On the one hand, she controls him; on the other, she seems to bear the weight of his “masculine genius.”&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:467.8663277511962,584.1252990430621,1322.2316088516743,386.099730861244"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1/b28cb493-e4b8-4a94-b73e-fe90d135ca1b","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:09:25.334Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds reminds Alma that for now they are “right here,” emphasizing that their future is not yet written, despite Alma’s plans and her eagerness to take narrative agency. His words emphasize the temporal twists the film has taken.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20327/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:68.86812200956939,68.98026315789473,369.67553827751186,256.59688995215305"}}}]}]}]}